# Langium Generate And Build

After code changes in this repository, run:

`npm run langium:generate && npm run build && npm run check`

Exception: If all changed files are inside `packages/extension/demos/` (excluding generator output), skip these commands — but still run `build:generated` when demo generated `.ts` or auth stubs change; see [demos-build-generated.mdc](./demos-build-generated.mdc).

If you changed **`packages/cli/src/generator/`**, follow [codegen-generated-quality.mdc](./codegen-generated-quality.mdc): `npm run build`, `npm run generate:all`, `npm run check`.

If you changed **`@core2ai/core/codegen`** (e.g. `renderStdioMcpServerSource`), rebuild in sibling **core2ai** (`npm run watch` or `npm run build`), then `generate:all`, `build:generated`, MCP restart. See `../core2ai/.cursor/rules/core2ai-build.mdc`.

If either command fails, fix the issue before proceeding with more implementation work.
